node.text:
Altitude training at 10,000 feet 🚴
So stoked to see my friends scoring down in Tahiti at Teahupoo. The waves look massive, wish I could have made it down there with them. Fortunately I’ve been working on the biggest project of my life and I can’t wait to show you what we’re creating. Looking forward to more big wave session with the crew soon! 
📸 @slaterneborsky

Growing up I idolized @robbynaishus1111, he was/is my hero, mentor and friend. A living legend that proved you can do what you love and be the best over a lifetime. I was honored to be apart of this film that documented his life. The trips were so so fun chasing the longest waves in the far corners of the world. 🌎🏄‍♂️ 
Watch “The Longest Wave” film on @redbull TV 
#thelongestwave #windsurfingdocumentary #windsurfing @joeberlingerfilms @chuckpatterson
